RootedWebComponent<T>
public interface RootlessWebComponent<T extends org.openqa.selenium.WebElement> extends RootedWebComponent<T>
Interface representing a web component without a root element.

This interface extends RootedWebComponent and provides default implementations for the methods to get and set the root element, which return null and do nothing, respectively. It is intended for web components that do not have a root element.
